              "text": {
                "content": "Work focuses on combining the trace data obtained from LMS logs and regularly used to predict performance with self-reported indicators often used to identify SRL. To do that, the authors perform a case-study on a sample of 145 students. Students perform a self-report assessment for SRL indicators and their logs are collected and analyzed.",
                "link": null
